      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOOK AT HER (4) was in the money two runs back before a good performance at her latest appearance over 2080m at Cranbourne, beaten 1.75 metres into third after being handy all the way. Meets a comparable field and she can figure in the finish. WESTERIA (5) has been close to the mark of late and again performed admirably last start, making up plenty of ground but finding one better over 2080m at Cranbourne. Tackles a similar assignment and she can go right on with the job. SPORTY ROCKS (7) last appeared when sixth over 1780m at Mt Gambier ten weeks ago. Look out for any positive market movement. BETTING ATTACK (2) is worth some thought despite his last-start seventh over 1755m at Echuca on July 7.",
